The paper deals with maintaining linear sketches in turnstile streams, which is a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The algorithm presented in the paper has implications for many streaming problems, which suggests that it may also be relevant to computational complexity (cs.CC) and data mining (cs.DM). Finally, the paper presents a new algorithm, which falls under the category of algorithms (cs.AL).
